heaviest_rainrate.status: The rain rate reached 27.0mm per hour on 02 September 2025, and resulted in 21.19mm of rain over 15.0 hours.  This is the highest rate recorded by our weather station.

summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 6.0°C), outside temperature (up 4.9°C), and inside temperature (up 2.6°C) and more moisture-laden rainfall (up 0.3 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 275 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 420 m), feels like temperature (down 3.4°C), and dew point temperature (down 3.4°C) when compared to today.
